rComments: very good teacher. wish there were more like her.

Prof. Greco's knowledge of Aristotle is very impressive.  She loves the material & was happy to answer questions. Lectures were mostly clear - her notes posted online were invaluable. The midterm was long (took me 3 hours) but was marked very fairly.  The class structure was disorganized at first, but did smooth out. Overall, a positive experience.
